---
layout: base.njk
title: Events
description: Screenings, rallies, trainings, art builds, and the rooms where this gets argued. Come to one — or send us yours.
permalink: /events/
---

<style>
  .ev{
    background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;
    padding:26px 28px;margin-top:16px;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:82px 1fr;gap:24px;
  }
  .ev.next{border-left:5px solid var(--gold)}
  .when{text-align:center}
  .when .mo{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red)}
  .when .dy{font-size:30px;font-weight:800;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.05;margin-top:2px}
  .when .yr{font-size:12px;color:var(--slate);font-weight:600;margin-top:2px}
  .ev h3{font-size:21px;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.3;margin-top:8px}
  .ev .where{font-size:14px;color:var(--slate);margin-top:6px;font-weight:600}
  .ev .body{margin-top:12px}
  .ev .body p{margin-top:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:#243247}
  .ev .body strong{color:var(--ink)}
  .ev .go{
    display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;
    letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--navy);
    text-decoration:none;border-bottom:2px solid var(--gold);padding-bottom:3px;
  }
  .tag{
    display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;
    padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;
    background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--slate);
  }
  .empty{background:#fff;border:1px dashed var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:38px;text-align:center}
  .empty h3{color:var(--navy);font-size:20px}
  .empty p{margin-top:10px;font-size:16px;color:var(--slate);line-height:1.7}

  .submit{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;border-radius:24px;padding:34px 36px;margin-top:50px}
  .submit h2{color:#fff;font-size:26px}
  .submit > p{color:#a9bad3;margin-top:12px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75}
  .submit form{margin-top:22px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
  .submit label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8fa3c0;margin-bottom:7px}
  .submit input,.submit select,.submit textarea{
    width:100%;padding:13px 14px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #ffffff2b;
    background:#ffffff0f;color:#fff;font-family:inherit;font-size:15px;
  }
  .submit input:focus,.submit select:focus,.submit textarea:focus{outline:2px solid var(--gold)}
  .submit option{background:var(--navy-d)}
  .submit .wide{grid-column:1 / -1}
  .submit .fine{grid-column:1 / -1;font-size:13px;color:#8fa3c0;line-height:1.65}
  @media(max-width:700px){
    .ev{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .when{text-align:left;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:baseline}
    .when .dy{font-size:22px}
    .submit form{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .submit{padding:26px 22px}
  }
</style>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Events</div>
    <h1>Come to a room where this is being <span>argued</span>.</h1>
    <p class="deck">
      Screenings, rallies, trainings, art builds, hearings. Organizing happens in person.
      It has never happened any other way.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">

    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Coming up</h2>

    {% if collections.upcomingEvents.length %}
      {% for e in collections.upcomingEvents %}
      <div class="ev next">
        <div class="when">
          <div class="mo">{{ e.data.date | mon }}</div>
          <div class="dy">{{ e.data.date | day }}</div>
          <div class="yr">{{ e.data.date | yr }}</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="tag">{{ e.data.kind }}</span>
          <h3>{{ e.data.title }}</h3>
          <div class="where">{{ e.data.location }}{% if e.data.time %} · {{ e.data.time }}{% endif %}{% if e.data.host %} · {{ e.data.host }}{% endif %}</div>
          <div class="body">{{ e.templateContent | safe }}</div>
          {% if e.data.link %}<a class="go" href="{{ e.data.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Details &amp; RSVP →</a>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <div class="empty" style="margin-top:20px">
        <h3>Nothing listed right now.</h3>
        <p>
          More <em>Rabble Rousers</em> screenings are in the works with New Economy Project, and
          there will be rallies as COPA and TOPA move. <a href="/#join">Add your name</a> and I'll
          tell you when and where.
        </p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="submit" id="submit">
      <h2>Organizing something? Send it to me.</h2>
      <p>
        A rally, a screening, a training, an art build, a tenants association meeting, a teach-in,
        a hearing you want people at. If it's about expiring affordability, tenant power, or
        community ownership anywhere in New York, it belongs on this page —
        <strong style="color:#fff">whether or not I have anything to do with it</strong>.
      </p>

      <form name="event" method="POST" action="/thanks/" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="event">
        <p hidden><label>Skip: <input name="bot-field"></label></p>

        <div class="wide">
          <label for="ev-title">What is it?</label>
          <input id="ev-title" name="title" type="text" required placeholder="Rally to pass COPA">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="ev-kind">Kind</label>
          <select id="ev-kind" name="kind">
            <option>Rally</option>
            <option>Screening</option>
            <option>Training</option>
            <option>Art build</option>
            <option>Tenants association meeting</option>
            <option>Teach-in</option>
            <option>Hearing / testimony</option>
            <option>Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="ev-date">Date</label>
          <input id="ev-date" name="date" type="date" required>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="ev-time">Time</label>
          <input id="ev-time" name="time" type="text" placeholder="6:00 pm">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="ev-loc">Where</label>
          <input id="ev-loc" name="location" type="text" required placeholder="City Hall steps">
        </div>

        <div class="wide">
          <label for="ev-host">Who's hosting</label>
          <input id="ev-host" name="host" type="text" placeholder="Your tenant union, coalition, or building">
        </div>

        <div class="wide">
          <label for="ev-desc">What's happening — and why should someone come?</label>
          <textarea id="ev-desc" name="description" rows="4" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="wide">
          <label for="ev-link">RSVP or info link</label>
          <input id="ev-link" name="link" type="url" placeholder="https://">
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="ev-name">Your name</label>
          <input id="ev-name" name="name" type="text" required>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="ev-email">Your email</label>
          <input id="ev-email" name="email" type="email" required>
        </div>

        <div class="wide">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold" style="width:100%;padding:15px">Submit this event</button>
        </div>

        <p class="fine">
          I read every one. Nothing posts automatically — I check it and put it up, usually within a
          day. If I have a question I'll email you.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top:56px">What we've done</h2>
    <p class="lead">Not a highlight reel — a template. Steal any of it.</p>

    {% for e in collections.pastEvents %}
    <div class="ev">
      <div class="when">
        <div class="mo">{{ e.data.date | mon }}</div>
        <div class="dy">{{ e.data.date | day }}</div>
        <div class="yr">{{ e.data.date | yr }}</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="tag">{{ e.data.kind }}</span>
        <h3>{{ e.data.title }}</h3>
        <div class="where">{{ e.data.location }}{% if e.data.host %} · {{ e.data.host }}{% endif %}</div>
        <div class="body">{{ e.templateContent | safe }}</div>
        {% if e.data.link %}<a class="go" href="{{ e.data.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">See the documentation →</a>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="note" style="margin-top:44px">
      <b>Why a screening, and not just a rally?</b>
      A rally tells people something is wrong. A film about Cooper Square tells them something else
      entirely: <em>that it has already been beaten.</em> Frances Goldin and her neighbours took on
      Robert Moses and five mayors and came out the other side with permanently affordable housing
      in the middle of the most expensive real estate market on earth.
      <br><br>
      People will fight much harder for something they've watched somebody else win.
      That's what the screening is for.
    </div>

  </div>
</main>
